Create "network" folder in C:/Program Files (x86)/Autodesk/Backburner/

Windows XP:
C:\Documents and Settings\USER NAME\Local Settings\Application Data\backburner

Windows 7:
C:\Users\USER NAME\AppData\Local\backburner

Edit nrapi.conf:
NetworkPath=C:/Program Files (x86)/Autodesk/Backburner/network

move backburner.xml to new folder: C:/Program Files (x86)/Autodesk/Backburner/network
